d of using `JSON.parse` is deprecated.The READTHEDOCS_DATA global variable will be removed in the future.--><script type=\"text/javascript\">READTHEDOCS_DATA = JSON.parse(document.getElementById('READTHEDOCS_DATA').innerHTML);</script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/_/static/javascript/readthedocs-analytics.js\" async=\"async\"></script><!-- end RTD <extrahead> --></head><body class=\"wy-body-for-nav\">   <div class=\"wy-grid-for-nav\">    <nav data-toggle=\"wy-nav-shift\" class=\"wy-nav-side\">      <div class=\"wy-side-scroll\">        <div class=\"wy-side-nav-search\" >                              <a href=\"#\" class=\"icon icon-home\">            sh          </a>              <div class=\"version\">                latest              </div><div role=\"search\">  <form id=\"rtd-search-form\" class=\"wy-form\" action=\"search.html\" method=\"get\">    <input type=\"text\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"Search docs\" aria-label=\"Search docs\" />    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"check_keywords\" value=\"yes\" />    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"area\" value=\"default\" />  </form></div>        </div><div class=\"wy-menu wy-menu-vertical\" data-spy=\"affix\" role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"Navigation menu\">              <ul><li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"usage.html\">Usage</a></li><li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"reference.html\">Reference</a></li><li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"sections/contrib.html\">Contrib Commands</a></li><li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"sections/sudo.html\">Using Sudo</a></li><li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"tutorials.html\">Tutorials</a></li><li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"sections/faq.html\">FAQ</a></li></ul>        </div>      </div>    </nav>    <section data-toggle=\"wy-nav-shift\" class=\"wy-nav-content-wrap\"><nav class=\"wy-nav-top\" aria-label=\"Mobile navigation menu\" >          <i data-toggle=\"wy-nav-top\" class=\"fa fa-bars\"></i>          <a href=\"#\">sh</a>      </nav>      <div class=\"wy-nav-content\">        <div class=\"rst-content\">          <div role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"Page navigation\">  <ul class=\"wy-breadcrumbs\">      <li><a href=\"#\" class=\"icon icon-home\" aria-label=\"Home\"></a></li>      <li class=\"breadcrumb-item active\">sh</li>      <li class=\"wy-breadcrumbs-aside\">              <a href=\"https://github.com/amoffat/sh/blob/develop/docs/source/index.rst\" class=\"fa fa-github\"> Edit on GitHub</a>      </li>  </ul>  <hr/></div>          <div role=\"main\" class=\"document\" itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Article\">           <div itemprop=\"articleBody\">               <div class=\"toctree-wrapper compound\"></div><img alt=\"Logo\" src=\"_images/logo-230.png\" /><section id=\"sh\"><h1>sh<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#sh\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h1><a class=\"reference external image-reference\" href=\"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/sh\"><img alt=\"Version\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/sh.svg?style=flat-square\" /></a><a class=\"reference external image-reference\" href=\"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/sh\"><img alt=\"Downloads Status\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/sh.svg?style=flat-square\" /></a><a class=\"reference external image-reference\" href=\"https://pypi.python.org/pypi/sh\"><img alt=\"Python Versions\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/sh.svg?style=flat-square\" /></a><a class=\"reference external image-reference\" href=\"https://coveralls.io/r/amoffat/sh?branch=master\"><img alt=\"Coverage Status\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/coveralls/amoffat/sh.svg?style=flat-square\" /></a><a class=\"reference external image-reference\" href=\"https://github.com/amoffat/sh\"><img alt=\"Github\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/stars/amoffat/sh.svg?style=social&amp;label=Star\" /></a><p>sh is a full-fledged subprocess replacement for Python 3.8 - 3.11, PyPy thatallows you to call any program as if it were a function:</p><div class=\"highlight-python notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">sh</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">ifconfig</span><span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ifconfig</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;wlan0&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">))</span></pre></div></div><p>Output:</p><div class=\"highlight-none notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span>wlan0   Link encap:Ethernet  HWaddr 00:00:00:00:00:00        inet addr:192.168.1.100  Bcast:192.168.1.255  Mask:255.255.255.0        inet6 addr: ffff::ffff:ffff:ffff:fff/64 Scope:Link        UP BROADCAST RUNNING MULTICAST  MTU:1500  Metric:1        RX packets:0 errors:0 dropped:0 overruns:0 frame:0        TX packets:0 errors:0 dropped:0 overruns:0 carrier:0        collisions:0 txqueuelen:1000        RX bytes:0 (0 GB)  TX bytes:0 (0 GB)</pre></div></div><p>Note that these aren\u2019t Python functions, these are running the binary commandson your system by dynamically resolving your <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">$PATH</span></code>, much like Bash does, andthen wrapping the binary in a function.  In this way, all the programs on yoursystem are easily available to you from within Python.</p><p>sh relies on various Unix system calls and only works on Unix-like operatingsystems - Linux, macOS, BSDs etc. Specifically, Windows is not supported.</p><section id=\"installation\"><h2>Installation<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#installation\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><div class=\"highlight-none notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span>pip install sh</pre></div></div></section><section id=\"quick-reference\"><h2>Quick Reference<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#quick-reference\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h2><section id=\"passing-arguments\"><h3>Passing Arguments<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#passing-arguments\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h3><div class=\"highlight-python notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ls</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;-l&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;/tmp&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">color</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;never&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span></pre></div></div><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"sections/passing_arguments.html#passing-arguments\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">Read More</span></a></p></section><section id=\"exit-codes\"><h3>Exit Codes<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#exit-codes\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h3><div class=\"highlight-python notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"k\">try</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>    <span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ls</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;/doesnt/exist&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"k\">except</span> <span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ErrorReturnCode_2</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>    <span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;directory doesn&#39;t exist&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span></pre></div></div><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"sections/exit_codes.html#exit-codes\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">Read More</span></a></p></section><section id=\"redirection\"><h3>Redirection<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#redirection\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h3><div class=\"highlight-python notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ls</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">_out</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;/tmp/dir_contents&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"k\">with</span> <span class=\"nb\">open</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;/tmp/dir_contents&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;w&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"k\">as</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>    <span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ls</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">_out</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">io</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">StringIO</span><span class=\"n\">buf</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">StringIO</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ls</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">_out</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">buf</span><span class=\"p\">)</span></pre></div></div><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"sections/redirection.html#redirection\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">Read More</span></a></p></section><section id=\"baking\"><h3>Baking<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#baking\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h3><div class=\"highlight-python notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"n\">my_ls</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ls</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">bake</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;-l&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"c1\"># equivalent</span><span class=\"n\">my_ls</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;/tmp&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ls</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;-l&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;/tmp&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span></pre></div></div><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"sections/baking.html#baking\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">Read More</span></a></p></section><section id=\"piping\"><h3>Piping<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#piping\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h3><div class=\"highlight-python notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">wc</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;-l&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">_in</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ls</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;-1&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">))</span></pre></div></div><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"sections/piping.html#piping\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">Read More</span></a></p></section><section id=\"subcommands\"><h3>Subcommands<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#subcommands\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h3><div class=\"highlight-python notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"c1\"># equivalent</span><span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">git</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;show&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;HEAD&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">git</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">show</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;HEAD&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span></pre></div></div><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"sections/subcommands.html#subcommands\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">Read More</span></a></p></section><section id=\"background-processes\"><h3>Background Processes<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#background-processes\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\">\uf0c1</a></h3><div class=\"highlight-python notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"n\">p</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">sh</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">find</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;-name&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;sh.py&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">_bg</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"kc\">True</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"c1\"># ... do other things ...</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">wait</span><span class=\"p\">()</span></pre></div></div><p><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"sections/asynchronous_execution.html#background\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">Read More</span></a></p></section></section></section>           </div>          </div>          <footer><div class=\"rst-footer-buttons\" role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"Footer\">        <a href=\"usage.html\" class=\"btn btn-neutral float-right\" title=\"Usage\" accesskey=\"n\" rel=\"next\">Next <span class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></a>    </div>  <hr/>  <div role=\"contentinfo\">    <p>&#169; Copyright 2023, Andrew Moffat.      <span class=\"commit\">Revision <code>4b980af3</code>.      </span></p>  </div>  Built with <a href=\"https://www.sphinx-doc.org/\">Sphinx</a> using a    <a href=\"https://github.com/readthedocs/sphinx_rtd_theme\">theme</a>    provided by <a href=\"https://readthedocs.org\">Read the Docs</a>.   </footer>        </div>      </div>    </section>  </div>    <div class=\"rst-versions\" data-toggle=\"rst-versions\" role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Versions\">    <spa